{
  "page": "A Storm of Swords-Chapter 69",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background-color:rgb(35, 135, 75)\">Jon IX</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> chapter</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_storm_of_swords\" title=\"A storm of swords\"><img alt=\"AStormOfSwords.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/24/AStormOfSwords.jpg/220px-AStormOfSwords.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"353\" class=\"thumbborder\" srcset=\"/images/2/24/AStormOfSwords.jpg 1.5x\" /></a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">POV</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Castle_Black\" title=\"Castle Black\">Castle Black</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Page</th><td>\n778 <small>UK HC</small> <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters_Table_of_contents\" title=\"Chapters Table of contents\">Other versions</a>)</small></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:rgb(35, 135, 75)\">Chapter chronology <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters\" title=\"Chapters\">All</a>)</small></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_64\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 64\">Jon VIII</a><br />↑</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_68\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 68\">Sansa VI</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">&#160;←</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle; padding-right:0.1em; padding-left:0.1em;\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jon IX</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">→&#160;</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_70\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 70\">Tyrion X</a></td>\n</tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n↓<br /><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_73\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 73\">Jon X</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Synopsis\">Synopsis</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_69&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Synopsis\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Mance_Rayder\" title=\"Mance Rayder\">Mance</a>’s raiders advance under the protection of a giant fortified <a href=\"/index.php/Turtle_(siege_engine)\" title=\"Turtle (siege engine)\">turtle</a> but the <a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a> is able to destroy it. Afterwards, <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon</a> tries to get some sleep, but is pulled out of bed by some men from <a href=\"/index.php/Eastwatch-by-the-Sea\" title=\"Eastwatch-by-the-Sea\">Eastwatch-by-the-Sea</a>. They bring him before <a href=\"/index.php/Alliser_Thorne\" title=\"Alliser Thorne\">Alliser Thorne</a>, and his new friend <a href=\"/index.php/Janos_Slynt\" title=\"Janos Slynt\">Janos Slynt</a>. The two accuse Jon of being a turncloak and oathbreaker, and they even use the captured <a href=\"/index.php/Rattleshirt\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Rattleshirt\">Rattleshirt</a> to support their accusations. Even Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Aemon_Targaryen_(son_of_Maekar_I)\" title=\"Aemon Targaryen (son of Maekar I)\">Aemon</a> cannot persuade Slynt to relent, and the former Commander of the City Watch has Jon thrown into an ice cell, relishing the thought of punishing one of <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Ned Stark</a>’s sons. \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character_List\">Character List</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_69&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character List\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" width=\"100%\">\n\n<tbody><tr valign=\"top\">\n<td style=\"width:25;\">\n<p><b>Appearing:</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Owen_the_Oaf\" title=\"Owen the Oaf\">Owen the Oaf</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Aemon_Targaryen_(son_of_Maekar_I)\" title=\"Aemon Targaryen (son of Maekar I)\">Aemon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wynton_Stout\" title=\"Wynton Stout\">Wynton Stout</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Pypar\" title=\"Pypar\">Pypar</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Grenn\" title=\"Grenn\">Grenn</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Dalla\" title=\"Dalla\">Dalla</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Val\" title=\"Val\">Val</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Satin\" title=\"Satin\">Satin</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Alliser_Thorne\" title=\"Alliser Thorne\">Alliser Thorne</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tormund\" title=\"Tormund\">Tormund Giantsbane</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Varamyr\" title=\"Varamyr\">Varamyr Sixskins</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Hobb\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Hobb\">Three-Finger Hobb</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Mully\" title=\"Mully\">Mully</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Hareth_(Mole%27s_Town)\" title=\"Hareth (Mole&#39;s Town)\">Hareth</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Kegs\" title=\"Kegs\">Kegs</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tim_Tangletongue\" title=\"Tim Tangletongue\">Tim Tangletongue</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Spare_Boot\" title=\"Spare Boot\">Spare Boot</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Cellador\" title=\"Cellador\">Cellador</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Janos_Slynt\" title=\"Janos Slynt\">Janos Slynt</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Glendon_Hewett\" title=\"Glendon Hewett\">Glendon Hewett</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Bones\" title=\"Lord of Bones\">Lord of Bones</a></li></ul>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:25;\">\n<p><b>Mentioned</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Mance_Rayder\" title=\"Mance Rayder\">Mance Rayder</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Robert_Baratheon\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Robert Baratheon\">Robert Baratheon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Red_Alyn_of_the_Rosewood\" title=\"Red Alyn of the Rosewood\">Red Alyn of the Rosewood</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Eddison_Tollett\" title=\"Eddison Tollett\">Eddison Tollett</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Othell_Yarwyck\" title=\"Othell Yarwyck\">Othell Yarwyck</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tumberjon\" title=\"Tumberjon\">Tumberjon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Watt\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Watt\">Watt of Long Lake</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Denys_Mallister\" title=\"Denys Mallister\">Denys Mallister</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Bowen_Marsh\" title=\"Bowen Marsh\">Bowen Marsh</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Weeper\" title=\"Weeper\">Weeper</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Endrew_Tarth\" title=\"Endrew Tarth\">Endrew Tarth</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Aladale_Wynch\" title=\"Aladale Wynch\">Aladale Wynch</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Mullin\" title=\"Mullin\">Mullin</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Zei\" title=\"Zei\">Zei</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jeor_Mormont\" title=\"Jeor Mormont\